Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.04,0:13:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So I spent months all day pretty much\Naround the clock meditating.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.51,0:13:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,One time I dropped something on the\Nfloor. I went down the floor and I
