Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,sitting right above black widow spiders\Nfor months and months and months on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Meditating. It's hysterical.\NWell, we both practice live and let
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.32,0:13:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,live, you know.\NSo, I guess live and let live is the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.83,0:13:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,best resolution. Live and let live.\NLet the black widow spiders be where
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.48,0:13:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,they are and you stay where you are,\Nwhich is not where they are. That's the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,best way to do.\NAll right. So, we'll go to the next
