Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.44,0:14:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. I forgot we were talking about\Nwhat's the lecture today about the uh
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.83,0:14:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the mystic. Oh, yes.\NWell,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.44,0:14:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the speaker today will describe\Nas best as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the speaker\Nis really an observer. The observer, the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,witness, the observer, the witness. So,\Nthe the mystic solemn uses the pronoun I
