Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.63,0:15:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,see,\Nso the pronoun is left out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.68,0:15:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's a detachment because what\Nyou're describing is phenomena from the
