Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,through non-conceptual\Nnon-conceptual thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.88,0:15:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So the way of Zen is to let go of all\Nconceptual thinking because it's all
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,judgmental and it's all illusory because\Nyou're only talking about perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're only saying about perception.\NAll right. So illumination. I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,if I've ever seen this. Have I ever seen\Nthis? I don't know.
