Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.28,1:07:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can love one animal easily as well\Nas another. And uh
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.00,1:07:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,so there's a lovingness for all of life\Nand all of its expressions.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.03,1:07:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh uh\Nuh bliss ecstasy
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.92,1:07:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you transcend the personal eye and you\Ntranscend the idea that there's really
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.76,1:08:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,separate others.\NThe word the personal eye as a pronoun
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.03,1:08:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't keep interfering all the time.\NWhy? Because you're you are now the
