Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.31,1:08:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're involved operationally but\Nthere's no cost involved.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.92,1:08:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The way it works is if you win, you win\Nand that's great. And if you don't win,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.31,1:08:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that's great.\NSo people get very passionate about
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.27,1:08:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,winning here and winning there and\Nwinning there. And all you can do is go
