Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.75,1:09:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,of the enthusiasm.\NIt's not going to change anything one
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.75,1:09:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,way. I've been rich. I've been poor.\NI've lived in the country. I've lived in
