Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.04,1:09:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're happy, no matter what's for\Ndinner, it tastes great.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.52,1:09:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,ain't so\Nbecause happiness and love transforms
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.96,1:09:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,everything into a positive experience.\NAll right. So you don't have anything
