Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.36,1:10:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,by letting go attractions and aversions.\Nletting go of attractions and aversions.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.76,1:10:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And the key to letting go of attractions\Nis the understanding that all
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.52,1:10:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,attractions are a projection of that\Nenergy field that was called glamour.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.19,1:10:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the best most helpful books ever\Nwritten that you imbue it you imbue it
