Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.15,1:10:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You think the attraction is in the\Ncheeseburger?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.15,1:10:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It's that you think a cheeseburger\Nis a wonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.76,1:10:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,For a person who doesn't like\Ncheeseburgers, they're not attractive,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.96,1:10:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,right? They hate them.\NIt's meat. Meat will kill you. Meat
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.15,1:10:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,causes gas on the planes.\NThat's one of the funniest things I ever
