Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.88,1:11:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,freedom.\NThings are done through purification of
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.04,1:11:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the will and all this comes about as a\Nresult of the illumination of the mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.44,1:11:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Unification with the with the divine\Nwhich we said is called uniommystica.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.12,1:11:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What is called enlightenment in Hindu or\NBuddhism
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.44,1:11:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,uh etc. in Christian theology is called\Nunionom mystica. the union of with the
