Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.80,1:12:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,S dissolves into the self with a large\NS. And every time it's happened,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.84,1:12:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,it's been the same. There is no personal\Npronoun. In fact, one has to learn how
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.04,1:12:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to\Num imagine one to the point that it it
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.92,1:12:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is at least an operational reality.\NThe world sees that you as a personal
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.84,1:12:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,individual self and I think as I've\Nrelated before one time when it happened
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.76,1:12:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,most profoundly\Nit took me a long time to get used to
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.44,1:12:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the altered state of consciousness. It\Ntook years actually. But the first thing
