Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.04,1:12:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know who the hell they're\Ntalking about. I had no connection with
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.00,1:12:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the body whatsoever. It'd be like to see\Na body sitting there and people were
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.36,1:12:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,talking to it calling it Dave. I said,\N"Isn't that strange? I mean why why are
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.36,1:13:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,they talking to\Nthat which I I'm I'm over here
