Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.67,1:13:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,transcending the levels of\Nconsciousness. This is the levels of the
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.36,1:13:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,500. So people, we got many people in\Nthese groups here that have come in
