Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.44,1:14:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,of 500s uh lovingness and then you\Nperfect the lovingness and the
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.48,1:14:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,lovingness becomes unconditional love.\Nunconditional love calibrates I think
