Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.80,1:14:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,540 is unconditional love\Nuh unconditional love it's typical of
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.80,1:14:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the 12step groups so when we calibrated\Nthe impact of various religions
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.96,1:14:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,on society\Nuh Christianity uh uh Judaism uh all of
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.28,1:14:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,them were about 450 uh and u the 12step\Ngroups calibrated at 540.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.92,1:15:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So the impact on society of the 12step\Ngroups is greater than that of the more
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.12,1:15:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,classic established religions. Why?\NBecause it is dealing with the nonlinear
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.44,1:15:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,unconditional love. And you know my\Nfavorite joke about AA
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.32,1:15:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and I know lots of people in the A for\Nmany years is this guy comes to a
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.12,1:15:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,meeting and he's crying and blubbering\Nover there. Somebody said what's the
