Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.15,1:15:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the guy says to him, "Yeah, but\Nthat was yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.08,1:15:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's profoundly the 12step group. That\Nwas yesterday. Quit blubbering today.
