Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.56,1:21:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,ulcer of 30 years duration\Nlife-threatening was cured in exactly
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.28,1:21:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,three acupuncture treatments.\NSo all the people that boo, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.15,1:21:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,boo boo and make fun of acupuncture as\Nbeing unscientific,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.80,1:21:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I say, well, just count your count your\Nlucky cards that you don't need
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.40,1:21:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,acupuncture\Nyet
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.56,1:21:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,because other days are coming. I hate to\Ntell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.52,1:21:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So u wisdom has spoke. Thank you,\Nwisdom. It said it's time for a break.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.44,1:22:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And how long does the break?\N>> About 15 minutes. about 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.12,1:22:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason we're five minutes late is so\Nthat all the people who are five minutes
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.80,1:22:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,late won't feel guilty about it.\NWell, people various things come up
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.56,1:22:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,about the mystic. So, we'll have some\Ninteresting discussion about it later.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.96,1:22:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The mystic is the closest to our\Nour approach to spiritual education.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.44,1:22:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What we've done in all the lectures and\Nbooks is really prepare prepare you for
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.08,1:22:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the mystical experience. We tried to\Nremove all the barriers
