Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.40,1:40:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And you don't uh so you don't tell God\Nhow you want it handled. You you turn it
Dialogue: 0,1:40:17.19,1:40:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,over to God. Sometimes the lesson is it\Ndoesn't work out.
