Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.63,1:40:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,paper and you mailed this to this\Ncompany and they mailed you false teeth
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.00,1:40:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and then he would whittle them. So I\Nspent my my his youth watching grandpa
