Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.67,1:41:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,teeth had to do with anything, but\NI don't ask God why he says other
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.19,1:41:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,things.\NIt'll be revealed
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.52,1:41:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,lying in bed and I'll get ah I see why\Ngrandpa in his false teeth came up.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.63,1:41:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is a positionality\Nyou're where your life becomes a
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.28,1:41:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,supplication and as I've uh said your\Nlife becomes the prayer. It's not what
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.19,1:41:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you do and not what you have it's what\Nyou have become.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.60,1:42:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All of all of nature knows who you are.\NAll of nature knows what you are and the
