Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.32,1:42:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is walking by and they know it.\NAll living things realize that those who
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.92,1:42:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,have aligned with God are aligned with\Nlife and the tree leans forward and then
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.92,1:42:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,goes back when that which hate is\Nhateful of life. Uhhuh.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.71,1:42:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I once went into an advanced state of\Nconsciousness in which all that became
