Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.67,1:42:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,things.\NOh god.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.00,1:43:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life then is a supplication in\Nwhich you are constantly asking by the
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.92,1:43:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,mudra by that which you are. You're\Nconstantly asking and opening to the
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.96,1:43:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,grace of God. Your openness then invites\Nrevelation to occur. Uhhuh.
