Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.88,1:43:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the grace and aesthetic beauty\Nof all that exists
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.67,1:43:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,eventually becomes a constant awareness\None's aware
