Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.36,1:44:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You begin to see the beauty and the\Naesthetic pleasure of all that exists.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.04,1:44:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the way people are dressed and the\Nway they do their hair and the way they
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.56,1:44:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,sit. And each one has their own unique\Nway of being in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.11,1:44:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's like you except you. There\Nanybody looks or is like you anybody
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.76,1:44:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,else like you either.\NThere's nobody like you. There's nobody
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.60,1:45:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,like any one of you is just stunningly\Nuniquely beautiful as you are. See,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:05.36,1:45:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that's why we're glad to see somebody we\Nhaven't seen for years. I haven't seen
