Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.36,1:45:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,your shoes. They're not giving you a\Nhaircut just that they are. Isn't that
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.36,1:45:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,right? There's a lot of people you just\Nfeel good because they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.40,1:45:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So you lighten up the world by that\Nwhich you have become. Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.88,1:45:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,your own spiritual progress serves\Nnot only yourself as far as reaching for
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.40,1:45:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,enlightenment, but it serves God and\Nyour fellow man. So the purpose of
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.28,1:46:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual work then is to serve God\Nyourself and your fellow men. Gloria and
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.96,1:46:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,excelsius.\NGlory be to thee, oh Lord, that my
Dialogue: 0,1:46:07.84,1:46:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,existence may be of service to thee.\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:16.80,1:46:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This lends a certain grace to one's\Npresence
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.96,1:46:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,without being aware of it. There are\Nsome people who around whom we somehow
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.63,1:46:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,feel better and then there's other\Npeople around whom we feel worse.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.04,1:46:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So you try to become one of the people\Nthat feel better around.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.88,1:46:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.\NHallelujah.
